ClassDesc: A request for inserting a @B_com#google#android#gms#fitness#data#Session_E@ and associated @B_com#google#android#gms#fitness#data#DataSet_E@ and/or aggregated @B_com#google#android#gms#fitness#data#DataPoint_E@ into the Google Fit store. Useful when data is read from a data source outside of Google Fit, or when inserting batch historical data. The request cannot have a continuing session, i.e. session should have valid start and end times. Request may contain multiple data sets and multiple aggregated data points. The Builder will enforce that each data set or aggregated data point represents a unique @B_com#google#android#gms#fitness#data#DataSource_E@. The Builder will also enforce that timestamps of the data specified are consistent with session start and end times. For all data points specified in the data set(s), the timestamps should fall between the session start and end times.
